  line `THE KAZIS ACT, 1880`
  line _________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line ________
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title.`
  line `Local extent.`
  line `2. Power to appoint Kazis for any local area.`
  line `3. Naib Kazis.`
  line `4. Nothing in Act to confer judicial or administrative powers; or to render the presence of Kazi`
  line `necessary; or to prevent any one acting as Kazi.`
